oracle.pg.rdbms.index.jdbc.handler

Class NoOpFileEntryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.rdbms.index.jdbc.handler.NoOpFileEntryHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileEntryHandler

    public class NoOpFileEntryHandler
extends Object
implements FileEntryHandler
    An Oracle implementation of Compass NoOpFileEntryHandler to support file level operations for the OracleJdbcDirectory directory under Lucene 4.5.
